Microchips used and connections

TOP, LEFT PART OF CIRCIT: Is a 555 timer beside it is a Shift regisiter (hc595) Besides that is 2 Binary Counters
MIDDLE, LEFT PART OF CIRCIT: Is a PIC16F877 (Yes i know its a cpu BUT its only emulating a ACSII to Binary incoder,Grouper) Besides that is 2 EEPROMS (AT28C256)
BOTTOM, LEFT PART OF CIRCIT: Is 2 EEPROMS (AT28C256) besides that is a AY-3-8913 (Sound channel Chip SCC)
